summary:
LETS PROTECT AND DEFEND MARKS AS JEWELS ! 
QUALITIES: Problems solving, analytic, strategic, team spirit, agility, creativity and sense of humor COMPETENCIES : •	Handled global portfolio of thousands of trademarks, designs and domain names abroad and in industries •	Managing a team of trademark experts in Switzerland and in the Netherlands • Expertise in IP procedures, copyrights issues and litigations follow up and license processes •	Broad experience in risk analysis process, leading marketing projects from IP perspective, clearance of a new company name, restructuration involving IP (mna, outsourcing, conversion of database), valorization of IP portfolio •	Specialist of non-traditional brands (company award), French and EU IP law and broad knowledge of counterfeiting Issues
